<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c674bd72f1fa67abf377d9ad5a7ab310ce872f0c","tid":1477932,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e29744df5e0d32366d773e410c474ed4a1cf0db0","tid":1477932,"uid":133277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"之前花木蘭有trailer 係大陸都係唔俾播 原因係呢個演員個樣太似維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e498b14e578eeaf3911935775d5ee88e0d35407","tid":1477932,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce2ffbd916c8f2dc9dc8bd55df3b1c15ce60699e","tid":1477932,"uid":10079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"小熊維尼咁巴閉嘅，做完熊又做人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:14:20.000Z","msg":"主席做廢老唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6c9fe2eff7a3bd2d919a61b1c7cc8a7d3c38cc","tid":1477932,"uid":282891,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:38:53.000Z","msg":"小妹獻醜了 please spread<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDear Disney,<br />\n<br />\nI have been a fan of Disney since childhood and I believe in Disney&rsquo;s power in bringing positivity and change for children and adults worldwide. However, it has come to my concern that Crystal Liu Yifei, the actress for the coming live-action Mulan, may not be the right choice to represent a character as righteous as Mulan. <br />\n<br />\nOn 15 August 2019, she reposted a criticism against the Hong Kong protestors on social media. In the past few months, over 2 million Hong Kong citizens have protested against the extradition law that may endanger the locals&rsquo; freedoms. However, the Hong Kong government has continued responding to people&rsquo;s demands with unlawful violence. Police brutality has become commonplace - tear gas and bullets were used thoughtlessly and there have been multiple cases in which the police SEXUALLY HARRASSED the female protestors (i.e. Hong Kong police removing a protestor&rsquo;s underwear during arrest). <br />\n<br />\nAs both a feminist and a fan of Mulan, I am aghasted by Liu&rsquo;s statement in support of the Hong Kong police, whose actions violate women&rsquo;s rights and human rights as a whole. Because of her support for the oppressors, I am doubtful about whether she is the right person to represent Mulan - an iconic character whose courage in the face of oppression inspires countless souls worldwide. As her action goes against Disney&rsquo;s mission to spread hope and positivity, I sincerely hope that Disney will reconsider the casting choice and give the world the Mulan we deserve. <br />\n<br />\nBest regards,<br />\nA Hong Kong citizen"},{"pid":"df36adb8c1932da2716dd5cf476f34b46f59bf0c","tid":1477932,"uid":133277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c674bd72f1fa67abf377d9ad5a7ab310ce872f0c","tid":1477932,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e29744df5e0d32366d773e410c474ed4a1cf0db0","tid":1477932,"uid":133277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"之前花木蘭有trailer 係大陸都係唔俾播 原因係呢個演員個樣太似維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"記錯咗 係唔俾comment先岩<br />\n<br />\n中國唔凖評論花木蘭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308134</a><br 